en: have any of the following Covid-19 symptoms? Fever, nasal congestion, new loss of taste or smell, runny nose, sore throat, conjunctivitis (pink eye), shortness of breath, new headaches, body aches, nausea/vomiting, diarrhea, or severe fatigue:

You may need COVID-19 testing along with quarantine at this time. For the safety of our staff and others, please do not schedule at this time. You may return to schedule if your COVID-19 test is negative or 4 weeks
sp: Fiebre, congestión nasal, pérdida del gusto o del olfato, goteo nasal, dolor de garganta, conjuntivitis (“ojos rojos”), falta de aire, dolor de cabeza, dolor de cuerpo, náuseas/vómitos, diarrea o mucha fatiga.
Las personas que anteriormente han tenido un resultado positivo de la prueba actualmente no son elegibles para las pruebas de detección de COVID-19.
